data.news_body:
We wish to inform you the Board of Directors of Zaggle Prepaid Ocean Services Limited (Company) at its meeting held today i.e. December 04 2025 has inter alia approved the following business(es):

1. 2. Investment of upto Rs. 75 Crores in one or more tranches in Rivpe (Investment).
